🚨 Missed the start of this week’s Q&A? Here’s what went down:

This week I went live with Dr. Sanchez and John Williams to share some important updates—catch up below!

1. GEN-AI Session Postponement
    * We planned to stream Dr. Sanchez’s Zoom alongside guest speaker John Williams on our LinkedIn page today.
    * Technical issues prevented dual streaming, so we’ve postponed the session on our Linked-in until after Dr. Sanchez returns from travel. 📅 

2. Admissions Update
• We’re onboarding volunteers only right now to reinforce our support staff and refine AI-agent automations.
• General admissions reopen May 26 for past & current cohorts—targeting 1 000+ members!

3. LinkedIn Live Expert Series
    * Launching a new Live series on our LinkedIn page featuring thought leaders in Generative AI across tech, ethics, business, and policy. 🎙️
    * Stay tuned for our curated roster of speakers—coming in the next few weeks! 

4. Community Spotlight Q&A
    * Next week (while Dr. Sanchez is traveling) <@1352785241252565174> will host a Spotlight session: we’ll collect the top 6 questions from the community about our future vision and current structure from WhatsApp & Discord. Dr. Sanchez will resume hosting the LinkedIn Q&As the following week. 💬

📪Attached are slides going over these points:
